<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_f1f22880-81bc-4efa-886e-b5e79594dcf7" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="SA"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>D4D5</sptc><title id="_0222ae4a-174a-43da-a912-2104a8217a67">Exemptions</title><archive-num>2019: SA D3.4(d)</archive-num><subclause id="_7d6f759d-287b-43e2-8bd4-b2bfe73d02cc" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_571edbe3-1260-48a2-95cc-b8342288c233">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p> The following areas are not required to be accessible:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_f2682fc6-1a9f-47e6-a594-cfd0c5191255">An area where access would be inappropriate because of the particular purpose for which the area is used.</li><li id="_33dc244b-77d9-48e5-bc57-ddbf24d548b0">An area that would pose a health or safety risk for people with a disability.</li><li id="_7ea789d7-74a4-4ad9-a358-ad986b4ae24a">Any path of travel providing access only to an area exempted by (a) or (b).</li><li id="_0503e401-3400-4fe8-baae-bdb993d79ea5">An area in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1271_2.5.0.xml#_0dbf918d-9dc3-4d70-9eb8-7172ea21c7a1" id="_6d8d4176-f932-4db2-a029-d9c140641c36" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">farm building</xref> and a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_55aea81b-51f3-4cc8-af61-c0915fecf62b" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref> where access would be inappropriate because of the particular purpose for which the area is used.</li></ol><p/></subclause></clause>